'''427''' was the designation of a group of three [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] that served in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. They were part of the [[Task force/Legends|task force]], led by the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Invincible (Strike Fear)|''Invincible'']], during [[Operation Strike Fear]] where they served as support for the [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] [[Warspite (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|''Warspite'']]. While mustering in the [[Dellalt system/Legends|Dellalt system]] they were identified as carrying military equipment by a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] reconnaissance mission flown by [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]] in a lone [[R-22 Spearhead starfighter|R-22 Spearhead]].<ref name="XWING">[[Star Wars: X-Wing (video game)|''Star Wars: X-Wing'']]</ref>

